sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>Service Account Token
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Router<br/>8033/8080/TCP
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as Client App
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    %% Model Deployment Flow
    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over User,ModelServer: Flow 1: Model Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply Predictor/InferenceService<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate<br/>TLS cert auth
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>Service Account token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment/Service<br/>Service Account token
        Controller->>etcd: Update model assignments<br/>HTTP unencrypted
        Note over S3,ModelServer: Storage Helper init container runs
        ModelServer->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>S3 credentials (AWS Signature v4)
        S3-->>ModelServer: Model files
        Adapter->>ModelServer: Load model<br/>gRPC unencrypted
        ModelServer-->>Adapter: Model loaded
    end

    %% gRPC Inference Flow
    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>ModelMesh: POST inference.GRPCInferenceService<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>No auth (optional: mTLS via Istio)
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Get model location<br/>HTTP unencrypted
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model replica info
        ModelMesh->>Adapter: Forward inference request<br/>8085/TCP gRPC unencrypted
        Adapter->>ModelServer: Inference request<br/>8001/TCP gRPC unencrypted
        ModelServer-->>Adapter: Inference result
        Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Result
        ModelMesh-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    %% REST Inference Flow
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 3: REST Inference Request
        Client->>RESTProxy: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8008/TCP HTTP<br/>No auth (optional: Istio)
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Convert to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC unencrypted
        ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to model<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
        Adapter->>ModelServer: Inference<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
        ModelServer-->>Adapter: Result
        Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Result
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>Client: JSON HTTP response
    end

    %% Metrics Collection Flow
    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Prometheus,ModelMesh: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Bearer token (kube-rbac-proxy)
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
        Prometheus->>ModelMesh: GET /metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP<br/>No auth
        ModelMesh-->>Prometheus: Runtime metrics
    end

    %% State Synchronization
    rect rgb(255, 255, 220)
        Note over ModelMesh,etcd: Flow 5: State Synchronization
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Leader election<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Update model placement<br/>HTTP unencrypted
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Cluster state
    end
